    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;Toy Shop Simulator&quot; 让你管理一家玩具店。组织货架，帮助顾客，并在一个有趣、充满玩乐的世界中扩展你的商店。加入我们的 Discord，结识其他玩家并分享你的玩具店体验！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/38b496be19104150ba129dda29cc8528.avif?t=1747472204\" width=640 height=73 /></span>从零开始打造终极玩具帝国。设计、管理和发展你梦想中的玩具店，在一个繁华的城市里，用你的创造力和策略取得成功。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/4365589a7fa9be795a75243556176b37.poster.avif?t=1747472204\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/4365589a7fa9be795a75243556176b37.webm?t=1747472204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/4365589a7fa9be795a75243556176b37.mp4?t=1747472204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/cbf9415c73d24364281ac8598eb318f5.avif?t=1747472204\" width=640 height=73 /></span>将玩具陈列在货架上，优化店铺布局，兼顾美观与效率，创造一个令人愉快的购物体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/d5f632cfb9994424129dd2fc01696b33.poster.avif?t=1747472204\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/d5f632cfb9994424129dd2fc01696b33.webm?t=1747472204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/d5f632cfb9994424129dd2fc01696b33.mp4?t=1747472204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/9a3bdaae0308b8ce3217386a1dd7b41d.avif?t=1747472204\" width=640 height=73 /></span>定制和装饰店铺的每一个角落，打造一个充满魅力的个性化购物环境。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/7ab102f4a9279af69814fda6656b9501.poster.avif?t=1747472204\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/7ab102f4a9279af69814fda6656b9501.webm?t=1747472204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/7ab102f4a9279af69814fda6656b9501.mp4?t=1747472204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/0037645a2c38545a3a679cb9b66bd33a.avif?t=1747472204\" width=640 height=73 /></span>从顶级品牌购买许可证，囤积各种玩具。为你的商店增添多样性，并随着每个新品牌的引入吸引更多顾客。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/3a6418bfc35c39b5f60a44ec259d876c.poster.avif?t=1747472204\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/3a6418bfc35c39b5f60a44ec259d876c.webm?t=1747472204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/3a6418bfc35c39b5f60a44ec259d876c.mp4?t=1747472204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/54cbcef750069c42dfb603e25f2f5a60.avif?t=1747472204\" width=640 height=73 /></span>扩大店铺的物理空间，升级内部装饰，并不断适应顾客的需求。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/bd075bc900864728195666e65828dc04.poster.avif?t=1747472204\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/bd075bc900864728195666e65828dc04.webm?t=1747472204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/bd075bc900864728195666e65828dc04.mp4?t=1747472204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/6416ae21e2b61162abccc3994b62a935.avif?t=1747472204\" width=640 height=73 /></span>处理并通过电动车交付在线订单，确保及时准确的配送。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/c535fbd30b44dec8b90f0c94628477b1.poster.avif?t=1747472204\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/c535fbd30b44dec8b90f0c94628477b1.webm?t=1747472204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163790/extras/c535fbd30b44dec8b90f0c94628477b1.mp4?t=1747472204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >功能特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 玩具交易系统</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 清洁机制</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > NPC互动</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 随机事件</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 广告系统</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 银行与信贷系统</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 安全摄像头与小偷防范</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 仓库与库存管理</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 充满活力的互动城市</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >投身于 Toy Shop Simulator，从零开始打造你梦想中的玩具店！</p>",
